tweet: Addiction is never sweet.  • 8 out of 10 youth who use tobacco started with a flavored product. • Many tobacco products come in kid-friendly flavors like caramel, gum, berries, and peppermint.  • Flavors mask the harsh taste of tobacco, making it easier for children to smoke.  https://t.co/sXg0Ly2ZR3
